<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Política de Privacidad — Sudoku</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

        :root {
            --primary:        #1A73E8;
            --primary-dark:   #1557B0;
            --primary-light:  #C5D9F8;
            --primary-xlight: #EBF3FE;
            --background:     #FAFAFA;
            --surface:        #FFFFFF;
            --text-primary:   #1C1B1F;
            --text-secondary: #5F6368;
            --text-muted:     #9AA0A6;
            --border:         #E8EDF7;
            --shadow-sm:      0 1px 3px rgba(26,115,232,.07);
            --shadow-md:      0 2px 10px rgba(26,115,232,.08), 0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,.04);
            --shadow-lg:      0 6px 24px rgba(26,115,232,.12), 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,.04);
            --r-sm: 8px;
            --r-md: 12px;
            --r-lg: 16px;
        }

        html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
            background: var(--background);
            color: var(--text-primary);
            line-height: 1.7;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        /* ─── HEADER ─── */
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, var(--primary) 0%, var(--primary-dark) 100%);
            padding: 60px 24px 72px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .header::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute; top: -50px; right: -50px;
            width: 240px; height: 240px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,.06);
            pointer-events: none;
        }
        .header::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute; bottom: -70px; left: -40px;
            width: 300px; height: 300px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,.04);
            pointer-events: none;
        }
        .header-inner {
            position: relative; z-index: 1;
            max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;
        }

        /* Mini sudoku 3×3 icon */
        .sudoku-logo {
            display: inline-grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 3px;
            width: 52px; height: 52px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,.22);
            border-radius: var(--r-md);
            padding: 7px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .sudoku-logo span {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 3px;
        }
        .sudoku-logo span:nth-child(2),
        .sudoku-logo span:nth-child(4),
        .sudoku-logo span:nth-child(6),
        .sudoku-logo span:nth-child(8) { opacity: .22; }

        .header h1 {
            font-size: 2.1rem; font-weight: 700;
            color: white; letter-spacing: -.5px;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }
        .header-subtitle {
            font-size: .95rem;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,.82);
            font-weight: 400;
        }
        .updated-badge {
            display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;
            margin-top: 18px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,.18);
            color: rgba(255,255,255,.95);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 5px 16px;
            font-size: .78rem; font-weight: 500;
            letter-spacing: .2px;
        }

        /* ─── LANGUAGE SWITCHER ─── */
        .lang-switcher {
            display: flex; justify-content: center;
            margin: -22px auto 0;
            width: fit-content;
            background: var(--surface);
            border-radius: 24px;
            padding: 5px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
            position: relative; z-index: 20;
        }
        .lang-btn {
            border: none;
            background: transparent;
            padding: 9px 26px;
            border-radius: 19px;
            font-family: inherit;
            font-size: .875rem; font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background .2s, color .2s, box-shadow .2s;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
        }
        .lang-btn.active {
            background: var(--primary);
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(26,115,232,.35);
        }
        .lang-btn:not(.active):hover {
            background: var(--primary-xlight);
            color: var(--primary);
        }

        /* ─── MAIN ─── */
        .main {
            max-width: 740px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 52px 24px 88px;
        }

        .lang-content { display: none; }
        .lang-content.active { display: block; }

        .lang-divider {
            display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 36px;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: .76rem; font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 1.2px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        .lang-divider::before, .lang-divider::after {
            content: ''; flex: 1; height: 1px;
            background: var(--border);
        }

        /* Intro card */
        .intro-card {
            background: var(--primary-xlight);
            border: 1px solid var(--primary-light);
            border-left: 4px solid var(--primary);
            border-radius: var(--r-md);
            padding: 18px 24px;
            margin-bottom: 28px;
            font-size: .935rem;
            color: var(--text-primary);
            line-height: 1.75;
        }

        /* Section cards */
        .section-card {
            background: var(--surface);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: var(--r-lg);
            padding: 26px 30px;
            margin-bottom: 14px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
            transition: box-shadow .2s, transform .2s;
        }
        .section-card:hover {
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
            transform: translateY(-1px);
        }

        .section-header {
            display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 14px;
        }
        .section-number {
            width: 36px; height: 36px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            background: var(--primary);
            color: white;
            font-size: .82rem; font-weight: 700;
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            letter-spacing: 0;
        }
        .section-title {
            font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--text-primary);
            letter-spacing: -.2px;
        }

        .section-body {
            font-size: .91rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            line-height: 1.78;
        }
        .section-body p { margin-bottom: 10px; }
        .section-body p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

        /* Custom bullet list */
        .section-body ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 8px 0 10px 2px;
        }
        .section-body ul li {
            position: relative;
            padding-left: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }
        .section-body ul li::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute; left: 3px; top: 9px;
            width: 6px; height: 6px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: var(--primary);
        }

        /* Links */
        .section-body a {
            color: var(--primary);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            border-bottom: 1px solid transparent;
            transition: border-color .15s;
        }
        .section-body a:hover { border-bottom-color: var(--primary); }

        /* Inline path highlight (Ajustes → Google) */
        .path-tag {
            display: inline-block;
            font-size: .82rem;
            background: var(--primary-xlight);
            color: var(--primary-dark);
            border: 1px solid var(--primary-light);
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 1px 9px;
            font-family: 'SF Mono', 'Fira Code', 'Consolas', monospace;
            white-space: nowrap;
        }

        /* ─── CONTACT CARD ─── */
        .contact-card {
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, var(--primary) 0%, var(--primary-dark) 100%);
            border-radius: var(--r-lg);
            padding: 26px 30px;
            margin-top: 28px;
        }
        .contact-card .section-number {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,.25);
        }
        .contact-card .section-title { color: white; }
        .contact-card .section-body  { color: rgba(255,255,255,.88); }
        .contact-card .section-body p { margin-bottom: 8px; }
        .contact-card .section-body strong { color: white; font-weight: 600; }
        .contact-card ul li::before { background: rgba(255,255,255,.6); }

        .email-chip {
            display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
            margin-top: 12px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,.18);
            color: white !important;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 9px 18px;
            font-size: .89rem; font-weight: 500;
            text-decoration: none;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.22) !important;
            transition: background .2s;
        }
        .email-chip:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,.28); border-bottom-color: transparent !important; }

        /* ─── FOOTER ─── */
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 24px;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: .78rem;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
        }

        /* ─── RESPONSIVE ─── */
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .header { padding: 44px 20px 60px; }
            .header h1 { font-size: 1.7rem; }
            .main { padding: 40px 16px 64px; }
            .section-card, .contact-card { padding: 22px 18px; }
            .lang-btn { padding: 8px 18px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════ HEADER ══════════════════════════════════ -->
<header class="header">
    <div class="header-inner">
        <div class="sudoku-logo" aria-hidden="true">
            <span></span><span></span><span></span>
            <span></span><span></span><span></span>
            <span></span><span></span><span></span>
        </div>
        <h1>Sudoku</h1>
        <p class="header-subtitle">Política de Privacidad · Privacy Policy</p>
        <span class="updated-badge">
            <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                <path d="M11.99 2C6.47 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.47 10 9.99 10C17.52 22 22 17.52 22 12S17.52 2 11.99 2zM12 20c-4.42 0-8-3.58-8-8s3.58-8 8-8 8 3.58 8 8-3.58 8-8 8zm.5-13H11v6l5.25 3.15.75-1.23-4.5-2.67V7z"/>
            </svg>
            Actualizado · Updated: Mayo 2026
        </span>
    </div>
</header>

<!-- ═════════════════════════════ LANGUAGE SWITCHER ═════════════════════════════ -->
<div class="lang-switcher" role="group" aria-label="Selector de idioma">
    <button class="lang-btn active" onclick="switchLang('es', this)">🇪🇸 Español</button>
    <button class="lang-btn"        onclick="switchLang('en', this)">🇬🇧 English</button>
</div>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════ MAIN ════════════════════════════════════ -->
<main class="main">

    <!-- ────────────────── ESPAÑOL ────────────────── -->
    <div id="lang-es" class="lang-content active">

        <div class="lang-divider">Español</div>

        <div class="intro-card">
            Gracias por utilizar Sudoku. La privacidad de los usuarios es importante para nosotros. Esta aplicación ha sido diseñada para ofrecer una experiencia simple, segura y respetuosa con los datos del usuario.
        </div>

        <!-- §1 -->
        <div class="section-card">
            <div class="section-header">
                <div class="section-number">1</div>
                <h2 class="section-title">Información recopilada</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="section-body">
                <p>Sudoku no solicita cuentas ni recopila información personal identificable como:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>nombre,</li>
                    <li>dirección,</li>
                    <li>fotografías,</li>
                    <li>contactos,</li>
                    <li>ni ubicación.</li>
                </ul>
                <p>La aplicación puede utilizar servicios de terceros que recopilan información técnica limitada necesaria para su funcionamiento y monetización.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- §2 -->
        <div class="section-card">
            <div class="section-header">
                <div class="section-number">2</div>
                <h2 class="section-title">Publicidad y AdMob</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="section-body">
                <p>Sudoku utiliza Google AdMob para mostrar anuncios dentro de la aplicación. AdMob puede recopilar ciertos identificadores técnicos, como:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Advertising ID,</li>
                    <li>información básica del dispositivo,</li>
                    <li>métricas de interacción publicitaria.</li>
                </ul>
                <p>Estos datos son gestionados directamente por Google conforme a sus propias políticas de privacidad.</p>
                <p>Los usuarios pueden restablecer o inhabilitar el Advertising ID desde los ajustes del dispositivo: <span class="path-tag">Ajustes → Google → Anuncios</span></p>
                <p>Esta aplicación no recopila ni transmite datos de menores de forma intencionada. Para información sobre privacidad infantil en publicidad, consulta las políticas de Google AdMob.</p>
                <p>Más información: <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">policies.google.com/privacy ↗</a></p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- §3 -->
        <div class="section-card">
            <div class="section-header">
                <div class="section-number">3</div>
                <h2 class="section-title">Consentimiento y privacidad (GDPR)</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="section-body">
                <p>La aplicación utiliza Google User Messaging Platform (UMP) para gestionar el consentimiento de privacidad en regiones donde sea requerido legalmente (como el Espacio Económico Europeo y Reino Unido).</p>
                <p>Los usuarios pueden:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>aceptar,</li>
                    <li>rechazar,</li>
                    <li>o gestionar sus preferencias de anuncios personalizados.</li>
                </ul>
                <p>El consentimiento puede modificarse posteriormente desde los ajustes de la aplicación.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- §4 -->
        <div class="section-card">
            <div class="section-header">
                <div class="section-number">4</div>
                <h2 class="section-title">Datos almacenados localmente</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="section-body">
                <p>Sudoku guarda información localmente en el dispositivo del usuario, incluyendo:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>progreso de partidas,</li>
                    <li>estadísticas,</li>
                    <li>configuraciones,</li>
                    <li>preferencias,</li>
                    <li>y récords.</li>
                </ul>
                <p>Estos datos permanecen almacenados únicamente en el dispositivo del usuario y no se envían a servidores externos.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- §5 -->
        <div class="section-card">
            <div class="section-header">
                <div class="section-number">5</div>
                <h2 class="section-title">Notificaciones</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="section-body">
                <p>La aplicación puede enviar notificaciones locales relacionadas con recordatorios diarios de juego.</p>
                <p>Las notificaciones pueden desactivarse en cualquier momento desde:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>los ajustes de la app,</li>
                    <li>o la configuración del dispositivo.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- §6 -->
        <div class="section-card">
            <div class="section-header">
                <div class="section-number">6</div>
                <h2 class="section-title">Seguridad</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="section-body">
                <p>Aunque se aplican medidas razonables para mantener una experiencia segura, ninguna transmisión o almacenamiento electrónico puede garantizar seguridad absoluta.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- §7 -->
        <div class="section-card">
            <div class="section-header">
                <div class="section-number">7</div>
                <h2 class="section-title">Cambios en esta política</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="section-body">
                <p>Esta política de privacidad puede actualizarse ocasionalmente para reflejar:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>cambios legales,</li>
                    <li>mejoras técnicas,</li>
                    <li>nuevas funcionalidades,</li>
                    <li>o cambios en servicios de terceros.</li>
                </ul>
                <p>La fecha de actualización aparecerá siempre en la parte superior de este documento.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- §8 Contacto -->
        <div class="contact-card">
            <div class="section-header">
                <div class="section-number">8</div>
                <h2 class="section-title">Contacto</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="section-body">
                <p>Si tienes preguntas relacionadas con esta política de privacidad, puedes contactar a:</p>
                <p><strong>ILL Support</strong></p>
                <a class="email-chip" href="mailto:ill.desarrolladores@gmail.com">
                    <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                        <path d="M20 4H4c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v12c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h16c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V6c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm0 4l-8 5-8-5V6l8 5 8-5v2z"/>
                    </svg>
                    ill.desarrolladores@gmail.com
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div><!-- /lang-es -->

    <!-- ────────────────── ENGLISH ────────────────── -->
    <div id="lang-en" class="lang-content">

        <div class="lang-divider">English</div>

        <div class="intro-card">
            Thank you for using Sudoku. User privacy is important to us. This application has been designed to provide a simple, secure, and privacy-respecting experience.
        </div>

        <!-- §1 -->
        <div class="section-card">
            <div class="section-header">
                <div class="section-number">1</div>
                <h2 class="section-title">Information collected</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="section-body">
                <p>Sudoku does not require accounts and does not collect personally identifiable information such as:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>name,</li>
                    <li>address,</li>
                    <li>photos,</li>
                    <li>contacts,</li>
                    <li>or location.</li>
                </ul>
                <p>The application may use third-party services that collect limited technical information necessary for operation and monetization.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- §2 -->
        <div class="section-card">
            <div class="section-header">
                <div class="section-number">2</div>
                <h2 class="section-title">Advertising and AdMob</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="section-body">
                <p>Sudoku uses Google AdMob to display ads within the application. AdMob may collect certain technical identifiers, including:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Advertising ID,</li>
                    <li>basic device information,</li>
                    <li>advertising interaction metrics.</li>
                </ul>
                <p>This data is managed directly by Google in accordance with their own privacy policies.</p>
                <p>Users may reset or disable the Advertising ID from their device settings: <span class="path-tag">Settings → Google → Ads</span></p>
                <p>This application does not intentionally collect or transmit data from children. For information about children's privacy in advertising, please refer to Google AdMob's policies.</p>
                <p>More information: <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">policies.google.com/privacy ↗</a></p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- §3 -->
        <div class="section-card">
            <div class="section-header">
                <div class="section-number">3</div>
                <h2 class="section-title">Consent and privacy (GDPR)</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="section-body">
                <p>The application uses Google User Messaging Platform (UMP) to manage privacy consent in regions where legally required (such as the European Economic Area and United Kingdom).</p>
                <p>Users may:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>accept,</li>
                    <li>decline,</li>
                    <li>or manage their personalized ad preferences.</li>
                </ul>
                <p>Consent can be modified at any time from the app's settings.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- §4 -->
        <div class="section-card">
            <div class="section-header">
                <div class="section-number">4</div>
                <h2 class="section-title">Locally stored data</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="section-body">
                <p>Sudoku stores information locally on the user's device, including:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>game progress,</li>
                    <li>statistics,</li>
                    <li>settings,</li>
                    <li>preferences,</li>
                    <li>and records.</li>
                </ul>
                <p>This data remains stored solely on the user's device and is not sent to external servers.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- §5 -->
        <div class="section-card">
            <div class="section-header">
                <div class="section-number">5</div>
                <h2 class="section-title">Notifications</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="section-body">
                <p>The application may send local notifications related to daily game reminders.</p>
                <p>Notifications can be disabled at any time from:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>the app settings,</li>
                    <li>or the device settings.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- §6 -->
        <div class="section-card">
            <div class="section-header">
                <div class="section-number">6</div>
                <h2 class="section-title">Security</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="section-body">
                <p>While reasonable measures are applied to maintain a safe experience, no electronic transmission or storage can guarantee absolute security.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- §7 -->
        <div class="section-card">
            <div class="section-header">
                <div class="section-number">7</div>
                <h2 class="section-title">Changes to this policy</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="section-body">
                <p>This privacy policy may be updated occasionally to reflect:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>legal changes,</li>
                    <li>technical improvements,</li>
                    <li>new features,</li>
                    <li>or changes in third-party services.</li>
                </ul>
                <p>The update date will always appear at the top of this document.</p>
            </div>
